<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_Beginner_BuildMode_StylingHome" s="314007">
  <T n="name">0xE845542D<!--String: "Styling Homes"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_StylingYourHome_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:eeba925104f71b98</T>
      <T n="text">0xB960CA09<!--String: "The right <b><font color='#199C2C'>styling</font></b> truly makes a house a home! Changing <b><font color='#199C2C'>Floor</font></b> and <b><font color='#199C2C'>Wall patterns</font></b>, customizing the <b><font color='#199C2C'>color</font></b> of furniture, and adding <b><font color='#199C2C'>decor</font></b> goes a long way. Just be mindful of your budget!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_StylingYourHome_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:eeba925104f71b9b</T>
      <T n="text">0x9DFBED3E<!--String: "Changing the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Floor</font></b> and <b><font color='#199C2C'>Wall patterns</font></b> of a room can give it a huge lift for a very small cost! \n\nFloor and Wall patterns can be placed one floor tile or wall at a time, or a whole room at a time by switching the setting above the Pattern categories."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\BuildMode\BuildMode_DesignTool_1.png" n="image">2f7d0004:00000000:695646c730767ee9</T>
      <T n="text">0xE491E31B<!--String: "You can change <b><font color='#199C2C'>color</font></b>, or <b><font color='#199C2C'>swatch</font></b>, on most Objects with the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Design Tool</font></b>. This is totally free!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\BuildMode\BuildMode_Eyedropper_1.png" n="image">2f7d0004:00000000:bf74da8b29b03fe0</T>
      <T n="text">0x94F4F9A5<!--String: "When you <b><font color='#199C2C'>extend</font></b> your home, you might find yourself with exposed drywall, missing windows, and mismatched roofs.\n\nThe <b><font color='#199C2C'>Eyedropper</font></b> tool allows you to click on something you <b><font color='#199C2C'>already own</font></b>, and then either <b><font color='#199C2C'>apply the same pattern</font></b> to an existing feature or buy a <b><font color='#199C2C'>new copy</font></b>, depending on what you clicked."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_StylingYourHome_5.png">2f7d0004:00000000:eeba925104f71b9c</T>
      <T n="text">0x46AADF64<!--String: "You can find <b><font color='#199C2C'>decor</font></b>, such as rugs and houseplants, by browsing Objects by Function and selecting <b><font color='#199C2C'>Decorations</font></b> in the dropdown.\n\nWhen the <b><font color='#199C2C'>value</font></b> of the decor in a room is high enough, your Sims will get a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Happy Moodlet</font></b> when they spend time there!"--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
